Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are looking to destroy \Nthe Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, \Nwho is after Shirahoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I join the Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin and the others who \Ndon't want to be pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can live in this country \Nwithout being chased
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the amnesty of the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go our own way, just like we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Pirates split into three groups
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shaking Fish-Man Island! A \NCelestial Dragon Drifts In!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:23.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FISH-MAN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe that this day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were the Celestial Dragons' slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were hopeless and all we \Nhad was hatred toward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got away from the Celestial \NDragons thanks to Boss Tai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but still they were looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought being a pirate was \Nthe only way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we can even go back to \Nour hometown without hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! No, Brother Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget what you've done for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, but we know what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needed the amnesty of the \NGovernment to help free us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you joined the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though you wanted to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit this chatting and go \Nto your family already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! They're becoming impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honey...\N--Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Baby...\N--Just go to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dad!\N--Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin, you were a slave just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you can get off of the ship finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will no longer be chased \Nas renegade slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us can stay with family without fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just like the mark \Nof the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of our terrible experience as \Nslaves, our hatred toward humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I understand what \NBrother Tai truly meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Boss Jimbei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is becoming a tool of the \NWorld Government... or humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he forget who killed Tiger-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost respect for Boss Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that there were many islanders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't like the idea \Nof me joining the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE RYUGU PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Jimbei's momentous decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now we have a relationship \Nwith the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to use this opportunity to \Nestablish friendly relations with humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep trying hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it's for his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Jimbei took \Non such a big burden-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he gets an order from \Nthe World Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has no choice but to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether he likes it or not-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will put himself in \Nharm's way and occasionally
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his blood will be spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Jimbei's sacrifice end up wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want you to \Nsuffer another hangover-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then something happened that would
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,change Queen Otohime's life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An uninvited visitor came to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugu Kingdom! Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is border patrol speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge wrecked ship is seeking \Nemergency entry into the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?! \NAccept them already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon is on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Send a rescue team immediately!\N--Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a Celestial Dragon \Ndoing on the seafloor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Celestial Dragon's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been attacked by \Nsome deep-sea creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look down on us Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come they were in such deep water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They are all dead! What weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a breathing mask now, you fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:05.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A WORLD NOBLE (CELESTIAL \NDRAGON) SAINT MYOSGARD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this Fish-man's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a mask now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and save my life, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no respect of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you ask somebody to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is a medical team here?\N--They're here but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they don't know what to do with "it."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the scum of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna work for the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or anybody, even if they beg me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Captain Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:10:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei is no match for me as \Na pirate in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no match at all, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on at the harbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, he said that a \NCelestial Dragon is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like his ship has wrecked \Nand he's asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun. Let's go see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't how it was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Fish-Man slaves \Nwent back to their island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it, My Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the thing, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fish-Man named Jimbei just \Njoined the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Sun Pirates which he belongs \Nto were hiding all those slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their evasion charges were \Ndropped by the amnesty of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Government so they went back home, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the slaves who escaped from \Nmy place are among them, My Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick to think \Nthat they are living a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,free and easy life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get them back, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've spent a lot of money \Nto collect those Fish-Man slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee! I didn't know that the deep \Nsea was such a horrifying place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, huh? Myosgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you address me without my title! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were my slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to come home with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give you my permission \Nto be free, fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill him, the \Namnesty will become void!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, fools! Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy admirals will come to the aid of a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragon in danger \Nin the world above.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people are afraid of your folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're on the Fish-Man \NIsland at the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the islanders stay quiet, \Nwhatever happens to you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll think it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I won't say anything!\N--Me too! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's barely alive. He's \Ngonna die soon anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him suffer the same \Nway that you slaves did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kill him!\N--Make him suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a respected man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the life of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do it!\N--Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, drop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Celestial Dragon \Nwho's ship was wrecked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mother rushed out of the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-sama, who are the Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are humans, Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a few humans out \Nthere and they are the scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard some gunshots too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otohime-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what he did to us in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He treated us like we were \Nanimals, not even slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your anguish - it's very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't plant your anger and resentment \Ntoward humans in children's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need a chance to meet humans \Nand figure them out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people on the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the tragedy we endured  \Nnor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Tai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a Celestial Dragon like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Queen of a fish country \Nis just another commoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or even less!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a mask and a doctor! Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Sea Kings!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look like a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi... Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the family legend, a long \Nlong time ago, there was a Mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who possessed mysterious power that \Ncould even control the Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken I decided to look into \Nthe legend and headed for the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestors! I finally found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi is the legendary Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Don't let anybody hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret legend that only \Nmy family knows, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can control the Sea Kings as \NI wish, I can do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have anything I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnap Princess Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I have to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still a kid now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... that's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me treat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few weeks later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the Celestial Dragon \Nwho's life has been saved was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about to leave for home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime did an unexpected thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get even with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm a respected \NWorld Noble, you insulted me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and harassed me terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fishes, I'll make you \Nfeel sorry for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what we get for saving his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We provided a ship and \Ncrew for him to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't let him go! It's \Ndangerous to this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you have more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll come with \Nyou to the world above.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the world above?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too dangerous, Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-jamon, Otohime! I won't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to negotiate \Nwith the Nobles, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure humans won't catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're the King and a Great Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is no point if \Nit's a strong man like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to show that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even a weak woman can \Ngo there and return home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we want to prove to our nation \Nit's totally safe up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm physically more fragile than \Nanyone - that's why it makes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more sense for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother-sama!\N--Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust the woman who you chose to be your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a fish queen - how arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is trust her and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime brought a single \Npaper back from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It represents a light of \Nhope for Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering numerous signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her dream becomes the dream \Nof all of Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Island seemed ready to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a gunshot rings out across \Nall of Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Sudden Tragedy! A Gunshot \NShuts Down the Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
